The architects have understood that the offices also need nursery school
The administrative building Avriopoint in Brno is the new head office of the company Arch. Design.
Nobody would say that he hides also in his interior a small nursery school with everything proper to such facilities: walls of colors, creative furniture and even a park in miniature in the exterior patio.
From October of last year, there can come to her the children of Arch's personnel. Design.
The company of architectural projects Arch. Design, of of whose study numerous buildings known about Brno went out, thought from the first sketches of the building Avriopoint of including a space for his mininursery school.
At the company about 90 persons are employed, principally at the age of the baby boom and they wanted to allow the architects and checkermen to be able to return soon to the work after the maternity.
Together with the possibility of enjoying a short time, the nursery school is one of the benefits that Arch offers. Design to his workpeople in the frame of his social program.
The constructors and architects this way have the possibility of combining a demanding profession with the care of the children.
The mininursery school was an idea of Arch's own personnel. Designu and, with the support of the direction, they managed to obtain financing of the European Union and of the Department of Labour and Social Affairs.
The mininursery school of the company is financed across the European Social Fund in the frame of the operative Program of human resources and employment, as well as of the state budget of the Czech Republic.
Thanks to the financing granted (an endowment of more than 2,8 million Czech crowns) they could buy the equipment and, after two years, hire qualified personnel and services.
When it exhausts the financing (two years), the company Arch. Design has the obligation to support in functioning the mininursery school with its own funds for three years.
The preparation of the project lasted one year and in the presentation of the request of financing he contributed the company Economy Rating.
The attention of the children is in hands of qualified personnel; also, there are present the whole day for his care a nurse and teacher of the Department of Education. The nursery school at present receives children without age limit, although most of them have less than three years.
Since it is a question of a "mininursery school," it can only receive simultaneously to a maximum of five children, although with the shifts they come more during the day.
The functioning of the nursery school is flexible to adapt itself to the needs of the parents and the children of all the workers have the same right to use the nursery school, independently of the hierarchy inside the company.
Although it is a question of an education and individual care, the contents of the program of the mininursery school are comparable to the program of the habitual preschool education.
In her the children not only play, but also they receive a quality education: from basic learning up to the preparation for the school, they teach up to English.
The class not only has toys and games of table, but also a computer for the children.
The presence of small children in the proper company to create a friendly and positive ambience.
The parents can go to see his children in any moment and avoid the stress of gathering late the children of the school when it is far from his work place.
This way, the parents are more productive while they work.
It does not turn out to be surprising that this generates of natural form an allegiance relation between the worker and his employer.
This way, Arch. Design is located between the companies they sign that they offer a big advantage for the admission of new workpeople: they support the family and, finally, this program reinforced the personnel marketing.
