The new procedure will have certain advantages for the applicants, between which they are:
The entire cost of proceeding with the visa will be minor, it will not be already necessary to realize a payment to coordinate the appointment, another payment to process the request of visa and another so that the courier service service delivers the document.
The applicant will only realize the only payment that will cover three services.
The current tariff will remain without change: the equivalent to 140 dollars for one tourist's visa, 150 dollars for cases of visas with request (including visas for temporary workpeople) and 390 dollars for visas of merchants and investors.
The persons who want to renew his visa will not have to come to an interview with the Consular officer, but they will only come to the most nearby ASC where they will present his documents and will take his traces.
Because the biometric information will be taken in the ASC, the petitioners who need the second appointment to be interviewed in the Consular Section, they will remain in this one less time than in the past.
The same way, who request visa in the Consulates in City Juárez, Monterrey and New Laredo already will not pay the extra tariff of service for 26 dollars.
